_sText: This is my first map. I don't really know how to upload a map, I know I could look up a tutorial but I'm too lazy. If it doesn't work, please tell me. I didn't add weapon spawns in this map, which is why I made it a GG map. It's a 12 vs. 12 map, but would probably work best with 4 vs. 4. Please leave a comment!
